# Instagram embed token (required for react-instagram-embed)
# 1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com and create an App (Consumer type)
# 2. Add "Instagram Basic Display" product
# 3. Go to App Settings → Advanced → Client token
# 4. Format: APP_ID|CLIENT_TOKEN
VITE_IG_TOKEN=

# Paste your token here, then copy this file to .env
